VAR-002: Sum of Two Numbers
Question: Store two numbers and print their sum.
Description:
Take two numerical values, store them in variables, compute their addition, and display the result.
Input:
Two numbers A and B.
Sample Input:
10
20
Output:
Display the sum of A and B.
Sample Output:
30
Constraints:
•	−10⁹ ≤ A, B ≤ 10⁹ 
Code :
a= int(input("Enter the first value "))
b= int(input("Enter the second value "))
sum = a  + b 
print (sum)

