VAR-003: Swap Variables (With Temporary Variable)
Question: Swap two variables using a temporary variable.
Description:
Given two variables a and b, swap their values by using a third temporary variable.
Input:
Two values a and b.
Sample Input:
5
8
Output:
Display the swapped values.
Sample Output:
a = 8
b = 5
Constraints:
•	A temporary variable must be used. 

Code :
a= int(input("Enter a value "))
b = int (input ("Enter b value "))
temp = a
a = b 
b = temp
print ("a is ",a)
print("b is ",b)
________________________________________


VAR-004: Swap Variables (Without Temporary Variable)
Question: Swap two variables without using a temporary variable.
Description:
Swap the values of two variables using tuple unpacking or arithmetic operations.
Input:
Sample Input:
15
25
Output:
Sample Output:
a = 25
b = 15
Constraints:
•	Do not create an additional variable. 

Code : 
a= int(input("Enter a value "))
b = int (input ("Enter b value "))
a=a+b
b=a-b
a=a-b
print("a is " , a)
print ("b is ",b )
