VAR-005: Area of a Rectangle
Question: Calculate the area of a rectangle.
Description:
Calculate the area using the formula:
Area = Length × Width
Input:
Sample Input:
10
5
Output:
Sample Output:
50
Constraints:
•	Length > 0 
•	Width > 0

Code :
l = int (input ("length of the rectangle "))
w = int (input ("width of the rectangle "))
print ("Area of rectangle :" , l*w)
